228
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:09,400
At Cheongsong Art Museum Director Kim Nak Chun's funeral,

229
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:12,280
mourners lined up today as well.

230
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:16,920
As the eldest son of Cheongsong Art Museum, the deceased, who has always practiced true noblesse oblige throughout his life,

231
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:22,200
