233
00:18:30,120 --> 00:18:34,520
There is no way to contain my sorrow at the shock of losing a giant in the art world

234
00:18:34,520 --> 00:18:37,640
and the eldest member of our family...

235
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,400
Just a moment, please.

236
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:42,690
I'm...

237
00:18:52,410 --> 00:18:54,880
I'm sorry.

238
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:57,530
There is no way to express the sadness and shock of losing

239
00:18:57,530 --> 00:19:00,580
the eldest member of our family overnight.

240
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:05,350
However, I, Kim Si Hyung, as Cheongsong's eldest grandson and as the representative of the bereaved family,

241
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:09,630
