242
00:19:09,630 --> 00:19:12,300
- and will carry out the cultural welfare projects he has been doing so far–
- Oh! Isn't that...

243
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:13,660
Jang Tae Jin's car?

244
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:14,880
Century Director Jang Tae Jin?

245
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,000
Oh, I think that's him.

246
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,100
- Jang Tae Jin!
- It's Jang Tae Jin!

247
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:20,170
I didn't... I didn't finish talking!

248
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:32,350
- Are you Director Jang Tae Jin?
- How do you feel?

249
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:35,290
Please say one word!

250
00:19:45,330 --> 00:19:47,020
I'm from...

251
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:51,520
Palda Auction.

252
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:58,100
